/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: interest-cohort=()

# Always revalidate every asset under /coverage/ so edits land for users
# without manual version bumps. Cost is one ETag round-trip per asset (304
# with no body) — negligible for the small surface each tool ships.
#
# Splat note: Cloudflare Pages requires `*` at end of path; mid-path globs
# like `/coverage/*.js` silently no-op. Hence the whole-subtree match. HTML
# under /coverage/ also takes no-cache, which is functionally identical to
# CF Pages' HTML default (max-age=0, must-revalidate). See CLAUDE.md
# "Cloudflare 快取策略" — future tools must add their own /<tool>/* block.
/coverage/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache
